{"id": "ChIJnd8drBjDwoARoIluPaLBA6M", "rating": 4.8, "userRatingCount": 87, "displayName": {"text": "Jam Jam Tea & Moments - Pasadena", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJnd8drBjDwoARoIluPaLBA6M/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tGbGFGRlNiM1Z6U0c1dVpHMTVNUzA0YTB0YVFWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I love the simple menu options they have. We got the coconut mango Pamelo at 100% sweet and Ube cheese foam slush at 75% sweet. Both were so tasty and not too sweet.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I love the simple menu options they have. We got the coconut mango Pamelo at 100% sweet and Ube cheese foam slush at 75% sweet. Both were so tasty and not too sweet.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Jessica Wychico", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100035825395709637541/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWHtwWUXh7D0LGFF65KAVRkmuzixOzc0HTcwuNXFiJCnAcnZACZew=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-26T04:08:39.286048664Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tGbGFGRlNiM1Z6U0c1dVpHMTVNUzA0YTB0YVFWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tGbGFGRlNiM1Z6U0c1dVpHMTVNUzA0YTB0YVFWRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c318ac1ddf9d:0xa303c1a23d6e89a0"}, {"name": "places/ChIJnd8drBjDwoARoIluPaLBA6M/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21jeE1ERldWa05tU20wNWFFUlhOVGhDU0VGa01WRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "This spot just opened. So let’s see if they’re pretty good eh or ew. I got their mango matcha and mochigome milk tea drinks to try. The mango matcha was not sweet and had mellow earthy matcha flaves complemented by a light fruity mango. The mochigome tasted like how a boba shop smells which I love. Perfectly sweet and milky. The drinks here seem to be more mellow here but are still lowkey pretty good.\n\nMango matcha $6.95\nMochigome milk tea $5.75", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This spot just opened. So let’s see if they’re pretty good eh or ew. I got their mango matcha and mochigome milk tea drinks to try. The mango matcha was not sweet and had mellow earthy matcha flaves complemented by a light fruity mango. The mochigome tasted like how a boba shop smells which I love. Perfectly sweet and milky. The drinks here seem to be more mellow here but are still lowkey pretty good.\n\nMango matcha $6.95\nMochigome milk tea $5.75", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "AC9", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114415861027882176583/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWiFfpOc9nsCcCI97_K0ntJYjx5NEVbNmjYETYfc21YuGhkhUgC=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-20T06:18:06.958211315Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21jeE1ERldWa05tU20wNWFFUlhOVGhDU0VGa01WRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21jeE1ERldWa05tU20wNWFFUlhOVGhDU0VGa01WRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c318ac1ddf9d:0xa303c1a23d6e89a0"}, {"name": "places/ChIJnd8drBjDwoARoIluPaLBA6M/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xOT2NtdENZbGN5ZGpKRWFrSlhhMmh5WTNkRk4zYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "A few days ago while shopping in Pasadena,\nI noticed that this tea shop had opened a new location 🥹\n\nAnd the location is honestly super convenient!\nThere’s a parking structure nearby that’s only $1 for the first two hours!\nThe shop is right on the main Pasadena street, and you’ll constantly see people walking around taking photos with their drinks haha.\nGetting a drink here after shopping really boosts the whole happiness level ☁️\n\nInside, the shop feels very clean and bright,\nwith a simple and comfortable atmosphere.\nIt’s also a nice place to sit and relax with friends for a bit.\n\nThis time my friend and I ordered several drinks 🤣\nand even brought some home for family too.\n\nHere are my favorites👇\n\n🥭 Coconut Mango Pomelo\nThe mango flavor is really rich, and the coconut makes it super smooth.\nThere are lots of toppings inside too!\nIt totally gives summer vibes.\n\n🍇 Green Grape Smash\nVery refreshing, with a natural grape flavor.\nIce cold and super thirst-quenching.\n\n💜 Ube Cheese Foam Slush\nThe cheese foam is rich and creamy, but not overly sweet.\nThe ube slush is super smooth, and it pairs so well with the slightly salty foam 🥹\n\n🫒 Crispy Green Plum Slush\nI was worried it would be too sour at first, but not at all!\nIt’s really refreshing and one of my recommendations!\nPerfect for hot weather after walking around shopping.\n\n🍵 Rose Cream Coconut Jasmine\nThe rose flavor is very noticeable, paired with coconut and jasmine tea.\nIt’s part of their Mother’s Day special drinks and honestly really good!\n\nOverall, there honestly weren’t any misses haha.\nAnd the location is such a huge plus.\nIf you happen to be shopping in Pasadena,\nyou should definitely grab a drink here 🤍", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "A few days ago while shopping in Pasadena,\nI noticed that this tea shop had opened a new location 🥹\n\nAnd the location is honestly super convenient!\nThere’s a parking structure nearby that’s only $1 for the first two hours!\nThe shop is right on the main Pasadena street, and you’ll constantly see people walking around taking photos with their drinks haha.\nGetting a drink here after shopping really boosts the whole happiness level ☁️\n\nInside, the shop feels very clean and bright,\nwith a simple and comfortable atmosphere.\nIt’s also a nice place to sit and relax with friends for a bit.\n\nThis time my friend and I ordered several drinks 🤣\nand even brought some home for family too.\n\nHere are my favorites👇\n\n🥭 Coconut Mango Pomelo\nThe mango flavor is really rich, and the coconut makes it super smooth.\nThere are lots of toppings inside too!\nIt totally gives summer vibes.\n\n🍇 Green Grape Smash\nVery refreshing, with a natural grape flavor.\nIce cold and super thirst-quenching.\n\n💜 Ube Cheese Foam Slush\nThe cheese foam is rich and creamy, but not overly sweet.\nThe ube slush is super smooth, and it pairs so well with the slightly salty foam 🥹\n\n🫒 Crispy Green Plum Slush\nI was worried it would be too sour at first, but not at all!\nIt’s really refreshing and one of my recommendations!\nPerfect for hot weather after walking around shopping.\n\n🍵 Rose Cream Coconut Jasmine\nThe rose flavor is very noticeable, paired with coconut and jasmine tea.\nIt’s part of their Mother’s Day special drinks and honestly really good!\n\nOverall, there honestly weren’t any misses haha.\nAnd the location is such a huge plus.\nIf you happen to be shopping in Pasadena,\nyou should definitely grab a drink here 🤍", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "kara yip", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112659566860958177165/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJtBomPV1RoRI_viBjDZ1TgeMb1mi9UDsEtu7UCCwkKP7-Kxw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-17T07:42:24.203099005Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xOT2NtdENZbGN5ZGpKRWFrSlhhMmh5WTNkRk4zYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xOT2NtdENZbGN5ZGpKRWFrSlhhMmh5WTNkRk4zYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c318ac1ddf9d:0xa303c1a23d6e89a0"}, {"name": "places/ChIJnd8drBjDwoARoIluPaLBA6M/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25KcFdtdENUREJNT1ZwV1dWOHhhMGR5WTB0Q1lXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Jam Jam replaced Sunbright in this location so went earlier to check it out. Very cute little spot, soft opening and nowhere to sit. A little pricey Like the vibe, got a mango pomelo and it was okay, would have to try more things on the menu to make a better judgement.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Jam Jam replaced Sunbright in this location so went earlier to check it out. Very cute little spot, soft opening and nowhere to sit. A little pricey Like the vibe, got a mango pomelo and it was okay, would have to try more things on the menu to make a better judgement.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Ying Liang", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116730976160866129316/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVRKgOGqtEKPpkTo8PoD9Op8tt3BnwKi8cEpUlvc4wsWAWGxug1=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-06T23:49:47.192665389Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25KcFdtdENUREJNT1ZwV1dWOHhhMGR5WTB0Q1lXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25KcFdtdENUREJNT1ZwV1dWOHhhMGR5WTB0Q1lXYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c318ac1ddf9d:0xa303c1a23d6e89a0"}, {"name": "places/ChIJnd8drBjDwoARoIluPaLBA6M/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT201cVFTMXJaREZVWVU4MlowZEJVekJCVlZWamRuYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I ordered tsubaki oolong milk tea, which is a spring limited release. The flavor is floral and fresh. My friend ordered brown sugar cream brulee milk tea with boba. Rich in brown sugar, creamy cream brûlée top but not overwhelmingly heavy. Very good for a quick afternoon stop! Love the aesthetic :)\n\nParking is moderately difficult, it’s old town Pasadena you know.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I ordered tsubaki oolong milk tea, which is a spring limited release. The flavor is floral and fresh. My friend ordered brown sugar cream brulee milk tea with boba. Rich in brown sugar, creamy cream brûlée top but not overwhelmingly heavy. Very good for a quick afternoon stop! Love the aesthetic :)\n\nParking is moderately difficult, it’s old town Pasadena you know.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Sincerely", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114349047098762479449/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUeOWQXwiMY5Qci7IxO2QFoK1nntnhzr9CoRFjKgtQimVT5uoU=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-30T21:36:28.140535699Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT201cVFTMXJaREZVWVU4MlowZEJVekJCVlZWamRuYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT201cVFTMXJaREZVWVU4MlowZEJVekJCVlZWamRuYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c318ac1ddf9d:0xa303c1a23d6e89a0"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJnd8drBjDwoARoIluPaLBA6M/photos/AWCwydgL3WUzOMPD5BHM7R0Sofa4wzwJB_xXGrfsL7fr0Q42qLxTc84Vbx1PgjAcwHY9jCa4P93I0kr5TA27T1vP7XOWNGjuZaz5k_7fbfliPBqWSxsGbHqLUf4dyI7Cb6TcY5t1FVk0G43if-4JZwa9RHKgV1hFsFQco6Yy76Ir8NrEuV-ox-DMa4ZxKpfykA3Y4NRsLhYW3K8GdtNUO-yc-4-KG-uWhgG8DeVuFCyNRqNq9i95wqjj6M65fBaUlsZmEer1odYo1OD9VZKtcTR00uMfzxx7wjP98TmOnDhnVZXyvveJO33Z0h78SKDzVV86GcEsuG0OLSrbxxN8x8QSiIn_ms_MVvq2HK68LIKDL5mf3wBm2HjqczW67Xq_2fR-RNwKXOFHo-UXu_4EYENbGh6KCrc89f70zJuuDO9N_UDp_pj4n_V6eTGcLbHtW3AP", "widthPx": 4800, "heightPx": 3600, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "Sincerely", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/114349047098762479449", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUeOWQXwiMY5Qci7IxO2QFoK1nntnhzr9CoRFjKgtQimVT5uoU=s100-p-k-no-mo"}], "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=!1e10!2sCIABIhCjsM_OSwzFX71jRBI4Tm9q&t=27&cb_client=maps_api_places.places_api&hl=en-US", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/place//data=!3m4!1e2!3m2!1sCIABIhCjsM_OSwzFX71jRBI4Tm9q!2e10!4m2!3m1!1s0x80c2c318ac1ddf9d:0